snippet: Gut racked up more Alpine skiing World Cup race points, finishing third on home snow in a fog-delayed combined event in Lenzerheide, Switzerland.
abstract: Lara Gut finishes third in combined event in Lenzerheide, Switzerland, running up her lead in Alpine skiing World Cup.
